### 품목 등록
POST {{base}}
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "의자",
  "code": "ITM-0004",
  "price": 10000,
  "unit": "개",
  "category": "MERCHANDISE",
  "initialQuantity": 100,
